notes.p: This is model is according to the paperToward a detailed computational model for the mammalian circadian clockIn this model only interlocked negative and positive regulation of Per,Cry,Bmal gene are involving.Some initial values are not given ,we choose them by ourselves in order to fit the curve in the paper.
Figure2A is produced by Copasi 4.0.19 and roadRunner online.
